          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Use this modifier to add a context menu to a view in your app’s",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "user interface. Compose the menu by returning controls like ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Button",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ",",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Toggle",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ", and ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Picker",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " from the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "menuItems",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " closure. You can also",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "use ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Menu",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " to define submenus or ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Section",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " to group items.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The following example creates a ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Text",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " view that has a context menu",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "with two buttons:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code" : [
            "Text(\"Turtle Rock\")",
            "    .padding()",
            "    .contextMenu {",
            "        Button {",
            "            \/\/ Add this item to a list of favorites.",
            "        } label: {",
            "            Label(\"Add to Favorites\", systemImage: \"heart\")",
            "        }",
            "        Button {",
            "            \/\/ Open Maps and center it on this item.",
            "        } label: {",
            "            Label(\"Show in Maps\", systemImage: \"mappin\")",
            "        }",
            "    }"
          ],
          "syntax" : null,
          "type" : "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "People can activate the menu with an action like Control-clicking, or",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "by using the touch and hold gesture in iOS and iPadOS:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [

          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The system dismisses the menu if someone makes a selection, or taps",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "or clicks outside the menu.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If you want to show a preview beside the menu, use",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "View\/contextMenu(menuItems:preview:)",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ". To add a context menu to a",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "container that supports selection, like a ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "List",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " or a ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "Table",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ", and",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "to distinguish between menu activation on a selection and",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "activation in an empty area of the container, use",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "View\/contextMenu(forSelectionType:menu:primaryAction:)",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
